==English==
===Tag===
'''[[has]]/[[have]]''' ''one'''''?'''<BR>

# ''[[request|Request]] for [[confirmation]] that converts a negative present perfect tense sentence into a [[question]]. Expects [[agreement]] in a "no" answer.''
#:<tt>“</tt>We haven't eaten dinner yet, '''have we'''?<tt>”</tt>
#:<tt>“</tt>You haven't been reading that nonsense, '''have you'''?<tt>”</tt>

====Usage notes====
As a tag, always used with an object pronoun substituting for the subject. Number distinguishes between ''has'' and ''have''.

